text: Andre Alexander Ramsey (born July 24, 1987 in Portsmouth, New Hampshire) is an American football Offensive tackle that is currently a free agent. He last played for the Baltimore Ravens of the National Football League (NFL). Ramsey played college football at Ball State University.
